            <link><![CDATA[https://t.me/guandianshuping/218]]></link>
            <description><![CDATA[<div id="page-content" class="rich_media_area_primary">      <div class="rich_media_area_primary_inner">                                                        <div id="img-content" class="rich_media_wrp">                    <h1 class="rich_media_title " id="activity-name">            马云落泪          </h1>          <div id="meta_content" class="rich_media_meta_list">                                      <span id="copyright_logo" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta icon_appmsg_tag appmsg_title_tag weui-wa-hotarea">原创</span>                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text">                                                                                    <span role="link" tabindex="0" id="js_author_name" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta_link weui-wa-hotarea" datarewardsn="" datatimestamp="" datacanreward="0">柳絮吃糖</span>                                                                            </span>                                                                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_nickname" id="profileBt">              <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight weui-wa-hotarea" id="js_name">                柳絮吃糖              </a>              <div id="js_profile_qrcode" aria-hidden="true" class="profile_container" style="display:none;">                <div class="profile_inner">                  <strong class="profile_nickname">柳絮吃糖</strong>                  <img class="profile_avatar" id="js_profile_qrcode_img" src="" alt="">                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">微信号</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">yzjyzj930705</span>                  </p>                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">功能介绍</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">仅提供一种不同的視角, 保持开放的心态，不轻信任何信息，独立思考得出自己的结论。</span>                  </p>                </div>                <span class="profile_arrow_wrp" id="js_profile_arrow_wrp">                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_out"></i>                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_in"></i>                </span>              </div>            </span>            <em id="publish_time" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text"></em>            <em id="js_ip_wording_wrp" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text" role="option" style="display: none;">发表于<span id="js_ip_wording"></span></em>                      </div>                                        <div id="js_tags" class="article-tag__list" style="display: none;" data-len="0">                                        <div class="article-tag-card__title">收录于合集</div>              <div class="article-tags">                              </div>                      </div>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            <div class="rich_media_content js_underline_content                       defaultNoSetting            " id="js_content" style="visibility: hidden;"><p style="line-height: 1.92;"><span style="font-size: 17px;">↑↓关注＋星标⭐，从此不迷路。</span></p><p style="line-height: 1.92;"><span style="font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><section class="mp_profile_iframe_wrp" style="line-height: 1.92;"><mp-common-profile class="custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe" data-pluginname="mp-common-profile" data-from="0" data-id="MzU5MzA2MDI5MQ==" data-alias="yzjyzj930705" data-headimg="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/H48iax2MFv6jJeXrO7BtHBL1GtFtficVRicxgfA1yEroQP1Kf6l3INJJczic61oick7I5UzvibOuNavI7TvEn7o5WWmw/0?wx_fmt=png" data-nickname="柳絮吃糖" data-signature="仅提供一种不同的視角, 保持开放的心态，不轻信任何信息，独立思考得出自己的结论。" data-weuitheme="light" data-weui-theme="light"></mp-common-profile><span style="font-size: 17px;">​<br>​</span></section><p style="line-height: 1.92;"><span style="font-size: 17px;">       突然发现最近马云的视频突然又多了起来，看来民营企业在媒体层面又重新活跃起来，这算是一个积极信号吧！</span></p><p style="line-height: 1.92;"><span style="font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="line-height: 1.92;"><span style="font-size: 17px;">       接着我刷到他最近接受采访的视频，再没有往日演讲时指点江山、激扬文字的风采，取而代之的是眼噙泪花，连声说“都难都难”。我有点感慨，看来三年来大家过得都难，这也是三年来民营企业经营状况的一个缩影。</span></p><p style="line-height: 1.92;"><span style="font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><section class="channels_iframe_wrp custom_select_card_wrp" style="line-height: 1.92;"><mp-common-videosnap class="channels_iframe videosnap_video_iframe" data-type="video" data-id="export/UzFfAgtgekIEAQAAAAAAMqcXnmBgbwAAAAstQy6ubaLX4KHWvLEZgBPE74MwfQRha4GHzNPgMIsm9E7FhUlCSHngrU6cie8v" data-url="https://findermp.video.qq.com/251/20304/stodownload?encfilekey=rjD5jyTuFrIpZ2ibE8T7YmwgiahniaXswqzGrjSdffcjOo0L7E5qIC9XhLwawbO4aVnKiaKLM4VCABOOIiaZOjbia1L8yQibosz5Via1ib6KQXX4TcoDxoeHM3s44cQ&amp;bizid=1023&amp;dotrans=0&amp;hy=SH&amp;idx=1&amp;m=&amp;scene=0&amp;token=x5Y29zUxcibCjVetS569ia23uhZOrOer0icvB4xn3PPKRYyCAriafIGnicOY4mMYibm1OpHaEukZ0QqxA" data-headimgurl="http://wx.qlogo.cn/finderhead/PiajxSqBRaEKgeaGcsugDvSbGg3SibKxC7ukibdvQGFOZZyCSaY34h2TQ/0" data-nickname="华商评论" data-username="v2_060000231003b20faec8cae38b11cad2ca02ea30b077641a3d63212cf76b4a087de921ab75b0@finder" data-desc="马云采访中一度哽咽，多次抬头止住眼泪：难，都难，现在都难，我的挑战再大也没有很多在岗位上的人大#马云#企业家#阿里巴巴" data-mediatype="4" data-width="1080" data-height="2048" data-nonceid="" data-parentwidth="320" data-weui-theme="light" data-isdisabled="0" data-errortips=""></mp-common-videosnap><span style="font-size: 17px;"><br>​</span></section><p style="line-height: 1.92;"><span style="font-size: 17px;">       我其实还是想回到2020年上海外滩金融峰会上，虽然距今三年，但感觉恍如隔世，马云再没有当年的意气风发，没有当年的挥斥方遒，我真的想看到他在演讲台上大骂“银行是当铺思想”，“如果银行不改变我们改变银行”。</span></p><p style="line-height: 1.92;"><span style="font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="line-height: 1.92;"><span style="font-size: 17px;">        毫无疑问，支付宝、余额宝的出现，逼迫银行不得不进行改变，提升服务质量和用户体验，我相信这点各位都有目共睹吧！</span></p><p style="line-height: 1.92;"><span style="font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="line-height: 1.92;"><span style="font-size: 17px;">        希望这种商业模式的创新不要止步于支付宝余额宝等，而是进一步激发民营企业的技术创新活力，真正改变和服务于我们社会。</span></p><p style="line-height: 1.92;"><span style="font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="line-height: 1.92;"><span style="font-size: 17px;">        马云落泪，不是英雄迟暮，而可能是一个时代的落幕，希望我们控制好幕布别让它落下来啊！</span></p><p style="line-height: 1.92;"><span style="font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><p style="text-align: center;line-height: 1.92;"><span style="font-size: 17px;"><br></span></p><section data-style='margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); caret-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;' class="" style="text-align: center;line-height: 1.92;"><span><strong><span data-style="outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-family: PingFangSC-Ultralight; caret-color: rgb(35, 21, 10); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" class="" style="font-size: 14px;">· END ·<span style="height: auto !important;"><img data-ratio="0.0967741935483871" data-type="gif" data-w="620" style="height: auto !important;" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/H48iax2MFv6iaziaNvAIRuquqtah02dWeK6jGuuTW1UutCibNJOypkptatJl5Aw2GqRg8gYicRicmtdMOGwcLAuyxl8g/640?wx_fmt=gif"></span></span></strong></span></section><section data-style='margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 0px